 Okay, Many of you seem to be interested in getting are melee those wonderfull gate potions, And for that I will tell your the tips of the trade! Or you can Visit KoE's site which has another walkthrough. <br>
<br>
For Starters You will need the Following:<br>
roughly 200 Flasks of Water ( not the foraged ones either)<br>
Roughly 200 Blocks of Clay<br>
Roughly 200  200 Medium Bowl Sketchs<br>
<br>
1) Combine 1 of each compent in a pottery wheel. (I suggest Thurg when you do this. all the ingredints are no more then 3 steps away, except for the water.)<br>
2) Destroy What you make<br>
3) Repeat steps 1-2 till skill is at 122 (This is what making bowls maxes out at. And all you need to make the potions)<br>
<br>
Now That you have your skill up.. Time to go Ingrediant shoping!<br>
What you need from mobs are:<br>
Crystilne silks (3) Drops form Spiders in Velks, As well in CC<br>
A glass Shard (2) Vendor purchase!<br>
Block of Velium (1) Velks spiders, CC orcs. <br>
**Hit Combine on the pottery Wheel!**<br>
when you hit combine you should get &quot;A unfire Velium Vial&quot;<br>
<br>
After The Unfired Velium Vial!<br>
You need a HQ Firing Sheet.(1) A Vendor purchase as well<br>
Unfired Velium Vial (1)<br>
**Hit Combine in the Kiln**<br>
You should now have a Velium Vial!<br>
<br>
And Finally!<br>
Next you have to go to Frundle Frenkler. ( The potion vendor in Thurg)<br>
And  Say &quot;what velium vapors?&quot; to receive a velium extractor. <br>
You put the following in:<br>
Peice of small Velium(2)<br>
and The Velium Vail (1)<br>
**Hit Combine!**<br>
You should now have your very own Thurg Gate potion!<br>
